# - Nutrition recommendations: $5/month
# - Meal parsing (text): $4/month
# - Meal parsing (photo): $150/month
# - Total: ~$319/month ($0.32/user/month)
#
# Supabase Edge Functions:
# - Free tier: 500K invocations/month, 400K GB-s/month
# - Expected usage: ~50K invocations/month (well within free tier)
# - Cost: $0/month
#
# WHOOP API:
# - Free (no usage fees)
# - Cost: $0/month
#
# Total Monthly Cost: ~$319/month
#
